Error: Error: Java.Lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java Heap Space

This Error Occurs When The Minecraft Server Tries To Use More Memory Than Has Been Allocated To It.

Solution: Step 1: Open the Minecraft server folder and locate the start command or server startup script (e.g. start.bat or start.sh).

Step 2: Open the command or script with a text editor.

Step 3: Add the following lines to increase the allocated memory:

For Windows:
```
java -Xms
